Thanks for the patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14978291" author="beobal" created="Wed, 28 Oct 2015 11:56:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, I&apos;ve updated &lt;tt&gt;CustomCassandraIndex&lt;/tt&gt; and committed in &lt;tt&gt;13e9fd55ff93c26ca339dfa30ed9ac7113894e8e&lt;/tt&gt;. There&apos;s also a dtest for this which I&apos;d overlooked initially. It wasn&apos;t checking the &lt;tt&gt;IndexInfo&lt;/tt&gt; table quite thoroughly enough to catch this bug so I&apos;ve opened a &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/riptano/cassandra-dtest/pull/630&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;pull request&lt;/a&gt; with some additional checks added.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
